				},
				"string" : "This page began its life as a {{gtPage:Project Diary|db=2j9m7db2i4oz116bexd7wbdxo}}. It spun out of [[wiki-client]] when I found two files in wiki-client libraries that {{gtClass:JSParser}} failed to parse. It also spun out [[Side quest: debugging JSParser]]."
